{"word":"G5346 - φημί - phēmí - fay-mee' - Affirm","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φημί</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phēmí</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fay-mee'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Affirm</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சொல்"},{"paragraph":"to make known one's thoughts, to declare; to say"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Properly the same as the base of <a href=\"#/G5457 - φῶς - phōs - foce/5457\">G5457</a> and <a href=\"#/G5316 - φαίνω - phaínō - fah'-ee-no/5316\">G5316</a>; to <i>show</i> or <i>make known</i> one&rsquo;s thoughts, that is, <i>speak</i> or <i>say</i>: - affirm, say. Compare <a href=\"#/G3004 - λέγω - légō - leg'-o/3004\">G3004</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}